OL,3,CProgramme listings for FRI 27 MAR
OL,4,G2100FElkie Brooks at the BBC
OL,5,     GTo mark her 80th birthday, Elkie
OL,6,     GBrooks looks back on some of her
OL,7,     Gfinest-ever performances at the
OL,8,     GBBC, including such hits as
OL,9,     GPearl's a Singer, No More the
OL,10,     GFool and Lilac Wine.
OL,11,G2210FElkie Brooks: Sight and Sound in
OL,12,     FConcert
OL,13,     GSinger Elkie Brooks in concert at
OL,14,     Gthe Hippodrome, Golders Green,
OL,15,     Gfirst broadcast simultaneously
OL,16,     Gwith Radio 1 in 1977. With a
OL,17,     Gspecial introduction by Annie
OL,18,     GNightingale.
